## 4. üé® Visual Polish & User Experience
We refined the "look and feel" to be premium and modern.

*   **"Too Dark" Fix**: Added subtle, animated **gradient orbs** (Indigo/Purple) in the background to add depth and life to the dark theme.
*   **Spotlight Effect**: Implemented a mouse-tracking light effect ([Spotlight.tsx](file:///c:/Users/akram/PhpstormProjects/portfolio/components/Spotlight.tsx)) that reveals card borders as you move.
*   **Performance Fix (The "Lag" Issue)**:
    *   *Problem*: The initial Spotlight component caused high Input Latency (INP > 500ms) because it triggered React re-renders on every mouse pixel movement.
    *   *Solution*: Rewrote the component to use **Direct DOM Manipulation** and `requestAnimationFrame`, completely eliminating the lag.

